<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Concaria Virtual Device and Dashboard</title>
  <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
  <style type='text/css'>
    .wrapper{
      width: 1000px;
      margin: 0px auto;
      font-size: 14pt;

    }
    .header{
      background: #00B0AB;
      font-size: 30pt;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .welcome{
      background: #eee;
      color: #000;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .button{
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 8px;
      display: inline-block;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .button:hover{
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #eee;
    }
    .views{
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
    }
    .redtext{
      color: #FF4833;
    }
    .column{
      width: 360px;
      float: left;
    }
    .red{
      background-color: #FF4833;
    }
    .blue{
      background-color: #00B0AB;
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body ng-app="concaria">
    <div class='wrapper'>
      <div class='header'>
      Congratulations! You now have your own IoT Connected Business
      </div>

      <div class='welcome'>
        Welcome to the fastest way to get started with the Internet of Things.
        <br/><br/>
        <div style='margin-bottom:10px; font-weight: bold'>Included in this bundle:</div>
        Xively CPM to model your IoT business<br/>
        Xively Broker connectivity platform<br/>
        Xively data storage to track product data<br/>
        Reference connected product and app<br/>
        Personal environment to test, learn, and scale<br/>
        <br/>
        <div style='margin-bottom:10px; font-weight: bold'>Here is what you can do:</div>
        Send <strong>messages</strong> to and from a product<br/>
        <strong>Model your business</strong> â€“ users, devices, apps, orgs<br/>
        <strong>Test</strong> your product features and usage model<br/>
        <strong>Accelerate</strong> your time to market, physical hardware, scale!<br/>
      </div>
      <div class='views'>
        Get started now by selecting one of the <span class='redtext'>two views of your business</span> below:<br/><br/>
        <div style='margin-bottom: 30px;'>
          <div class='column'>
            <img src='/manage/img/user.png' alt='user'/>
          </div>
          <div class='column' style='height: 150px; margin-top: 50px; width: 230px; text-align: center;'>
            <a class='button red' href="/manage/#/device/<%= virtualdevice.mqtt.deviceId %>?demo=1" target="_blank">End User View</a>
          </div>
          <div class='column' style='margin-top: 30px; height: 200px;'>
            <strong>View one connected product and the end user app</strong> to control the product and see product data and status
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style='margin-bottom: 50px;'>
          <div class='column'>
            <img src='/manage/img/company.png' alt='company' style='width: 377px; height: auto;'/>
            <br/><br/><br/>
          </div>
          <div class='column' style='height: 150px; margin-top: 140px; width: 230px; text-align: center;'>
            <a class='button red' href="/manage/" target="_blank">Business View</a>
          </div>
          <div class='column' style='margin-top: 110px; height: 350px;'>
            <strong>View a dashboard of all connected products, users and organizational structure,</strong> to set-up, manage and run your connected business
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style='text-align: center'>
          <a class='button blue' href='https://blog.xively.com/introducing-concaria/' style='width: 200px;'>Learn more about Concaria and Xively</a>
          <br/><br/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
